      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "おはようございます、昨夜はライブだったのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning. Why are you up so early‚ even after",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "どうしてこんなに早起きなんですか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "last night’s live?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "まったくですわ、オフの日くらいゆっくり",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s too much. On a day off‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.766666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "眠らせてほしいので――ふわっ……、くー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "at least let me sleep… Zzz… zzz…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.53333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "凄い、すずちゃん、立ったまま眠ってる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow. Suzu-chan is sleeping standing up…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.866666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あはは、元気なのが芽衣の取柄だからねー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahaha. Because being lively is what I do best!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "それより大事なお話があるの、みんな座って座って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I have something more important to talk about. Sit down‚ all of you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.43333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "大事な話？　何？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Something important? What is it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "{user}さんがさとみちゃんと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san was chatting",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
